4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior experience. The bootcamp lasts 16 weeks with three live online classes weekly and accommodates up to 16 students per class. Participants will build a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, and network/server administration, focusing on cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Graduates will earn an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Instruction is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop